WEBVTT

00:00:29.099 --> 00:00:31.909
to close the digital divide,

00:00:31.933 --> 00:00:36.114
and also to allow for what we call
"The Internet of Things" --

00:00:36.138 --> 00:00:39.304
tens of billions of devices
connected to the Internet.

00:00:39.328 --> 00:00:43.359
In my view, such an extension
of the Internet can only work

00:00:43.383 --> 00:00:45.730
if it's almost energy-neutral.

00:00:46.173 --> 00:00:51.005
This means we need to use existing
infrastructure as much as possible.

00:00:51.497 --> 00:00:56.434
And this is where the solar cell
and the LED come in.

00:00:56.959 --> 00:00:59.277
I demonstrated for the first time,

00:00:59.301 --> 00:01:01.266
at TED in 2011,